<h1>hunchentoot-cgi</h1>

<p>A library for executing CGI scripts from the hunchentoot webserver
written by Cyrus Harmon.</p>

<p>To activate hunchentoot-cgi, create a new dispatcher-and-handler and
add this to the hunchentoot global dispatch table roughly as follows:</p>

<pre><code>(pushnew (hunchentoot-cgi:create-cgi-dispatcher-and-handler
          &quot;/cgi-bin/&quot;
          &quot;/usr/local/share/hunchentoot/cgi/&quot;
         hunchentoot:*dispatch-table*
         :test #'equal)
</code></pre>

<p>This will instruct hunchentoot to field requests to /cgi-bin/foo
and execute /usr/local/share/hunchentoot/cgi/foo as a CGI script.</p>
